== Overview ==
The TXc1 Turbo Laser is an extremely deadly weapon system capable of concentrating successive laser beams into a single target or delivering less amounts to multiple weaker targets.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Turbo Laser can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Radial Laser Technology]].
